<div class="bg-light py-5 border-bottom position-relative overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9 0%, #ffffff 100%); min-height: 80vh; display: flex; align-items: center;">
  <div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row align-items-center g-5">

      <div class="col-lg-6 text-center text-lg-start">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start mb-4">
          <div class="bg-success text-white rounded-3 p-3 shadow-sm d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
            <i class="fas fa-leaf fs-2"></i>
          </div>
          <span class="ms-3 fw-bold text-success text-uppercase tracking-wider small">Plant Care App</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-dark mb-3 lh-sm">
          Get Expert AI Advice, <br>
          <span class="text-success">Master Your Plant's Health.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="lead text-muted mb-5">
          A professional plant care app to help you never forget to water or fertilize. Connect with our expert AI assistant for disease diagnosis through photo uploads, care recommendations and weather-synchronized guidance. Perfect for your home, your balcony and your garden.
        </p>

        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row gap-3 justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start">
          <% if user_signed_in? %>
            <%= link_to "Go to My Dashboard 🌱", plants_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg px-5 rounded-pill fw-semibold shadow" %>
          <% else %>
            <%= link_to "Get Started", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-success btn-lg px-5 rounded-pill fw-semibold shadow" %>
            <%= link_to "Create Account", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4 rounded-pill fw-semibold" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
        <div class="position-relative d-inline-block">
          <div class="bg-success opacity-10 position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle rounded-circle" style="width: 120%; height: 120%; filter: blur(50px);"></div>

          <div class="card shadow-lg border-0 rounded-3 text-start position-relative flex-column" style="max-width: 450px; margin: 0 auto; min-height: 400px; display: flex;">

            <div class="card-header bg-success text-white fw-bold py-3 border-0 rounded-top-3 d-flex align-items-center">
              <span class="fs-5 me-2">🤖</span> Chat with AI Assistant
            </div>

            <div class="card-body bg-light overflow-auto p-4 flex-grow-1" style="max-height: 280px;">

              <div class="d-flex mb-3 justify-content-start">
                <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-3 shadow-sm border" style="max-width: 85%;">
                  <p class="mb-0 small text-dark fw-semibold text-success mb-1">Tommy (Tomato)</p>
                  <p class="mb-0 small text-muted">Hi Desiree! I noticed heavy rain is expected in Schifferstadt today. Hold off on watering me, nature has it covered!</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="d-flex mb-3 justify-content-start">
                <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-3 shadow-sm border" style="max-width: 85%;">
                  <p class="mb-0 small text-dark fw-semibold text-success mb-1">Diagnosis Bot</p>
                  <p class="mb-0 small text-muted">That photo shows early signs of late blight. I recommend increasing airflow and removing affected leaves immediately.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>

            <div class="card-footer bg-white p-3 border-top rounded-bottom-3 mt-auto">
              <div class="input-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-control rounded-pill-start border-success" placeholder="Ask about disease or care..." aria-label="Plant question" disabled>
                <button class="btn btn-success rounded-pill-end px-4 fw-semibold" type="button" disabled>Send</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container py-5 my-5">
  <div class="text-center max-w-xl mx-auto mb-5">
    <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark">How our AI Assistant helps you</h2>
    <p class="text-muted">Smart, proactive care for your entire plant family.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row g-4 text-center">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-3 h-100 bg-white shadow-sm border">
        <div class="text-success fs-1 mb-3">📸</div>
        <h4 class="fw-bold h5">Photo Diagnosis</h4>
        <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Upload photos of wilting or diseased plants. Our AI quickly identifies issues and provides actionable treatment plans.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-3 h-100 bg-white shadow-sm border">
        <div class="text-success fs-1 mb-3">🌤️</div>
        <h4 class="fw-bold h5">Weather-Smart Reminders</h4>
        <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Never miss watering or fertilizing. Outdoor plants get personalized care tips based on local weather forecasts and photo analysis.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-3 h-100 bg-white shadow-sm border">
        <div class="text-success fs-1 mb-3">🏡</div>
        <h4 class="fw-bold h5">Total Care Tracking</h4>
        <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Keep your plants thriving effortlessly. The app adapts seamlessly to your specific spaces, matching care timelines for indoor and outdoor environments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
